  description: 'Increases Magic Resist by 5 and Health by 40. Grants "Molten Aura":
    Every second, the wearer radiates intense heat, applying the Burned status effect
    to all enemies within 2 hexes. An armor of shimmering, brass-colored links that
    glow with internal heat; it radiates a searing wave of warmth that melts steel
    and bone, turning the battlefield around its wearer into a living furnace.'
